14:24:48.577 [MainThread] INFO    thonny.running: Prepared clean state for executing ToplevelCommand(args=['-c'], args_str='-c $EDITOR_CONTENT', cmd_line='%Run -c $EDITOR_CONTENT', tty_mode=True, source='import time\nfrom machine import Pin, SPI\n\n# Simple test - fill entire display with black\nEPD_M1_CS_PIN = 1\nEPD_M2S2_DC_PIN = 27\n\n# Init SPI and pins\nspi = SPI(0, baudrate=2000000, polarity=0, phase=0, sck=Pin(2), mosi=Pin(3))\ncs = Pin(EPD_M1_CS_PIN, Pin.OUT, value=1)\ndc = Pin(EPD_M2S2_DC_PIN, Pin.OUT)\nrst = Pin(21, Pin.OUT)\n\n# Reset\nrst.value(0)\ntime.sleep_ms(10)\nrst.value(1)\ntime.sleep_ms(200)\n\n# Send command\ndef cmd(c):\n    dc.value(0)\n    cs.value(0)\n    spi.write(bytearray([c]))\n    cs.value(1)\n\n# Send data\ndef data(d):\n    dc.value(1)\n    cs.value(0)\n    spi.write(bytearray([d]))\n    cs.value(1)\n\n# Init M1 panel\ncmd(0x00)  # Panel setting\ndata(0x0f)\n\ncmd(0x61)  # Resolution\ndata(0x02)\ndata(0x88)\ndata(0x01)\ndata(0xEC)\n\n# Fill black (0x00 = black)\ncmd(0x10)\nfor i in range(81 * 492):\n    data(0x00)\n\ncmd(0x13)\nfor i in range(81 * 492):\n    data(0xFF)\n\n# Power on and refresh\ncmd(0x04)\ntime.sleep_ms(300)\ncmd(0x12)\n\nprint("Done - check display")', name='Run', argv=[], id='cmd_65', local_cwd='/home/ironick')
