14:25:55.902 [MainThread] INFO    thonny.running: Prepared clean state for executing ToplevelCommand(args=['-c'], args_str='-c $EDITOR_CONTENT', cmd_line='%Run -c $EDITOR_CONTENT', tty_mode=True, source='import time\nfrom machine import Pin, SPI\n\n# Setup\nspi = SPI(0, baudrate=2000000, polarity=0, phase=0, sck=Pin(2), mosi=Pin(3))\nm1_cs = Pin(1, Pin.OUT, value=1)\ndc = Pin(26, Pin.OUT)\nrst = Pin(21, Pin.OUT)\nbusy = Pin(20, Pin.IN)\n\n# Reset\nrst.value(1)\ntime.sleep_ms(200)\nrst.value(0)\ntime.sleep_ms(10)\nrst.value(1)\ntime.sleep_ms(200)\n\ndef cmd(c):\n    dc.value(0)\n    m1_cs.value(0)\n    spi.write(bytearray([c]))\n    m1_cs.value(1)\n\ndef data(d):\n    dc.value(1)\n    m1_cs.value(0)\n    spi.write(bytearray([d]))\n    m1_cs.value(1)\n\ndef wait_busy():\n    cmd(0x71)\n    timeout = 5000\n    start = time.ticks_ms()\n    while busy.value() == 0:\n        if time.ticks_diff(time.ticks_ms(), start) > timeout:\n            print("Timeout!")\n            break\n        time.sleep_ms(10)\n\n# Init\ncmd(0x00)\ndata(0x0f)\n\n# Fill white (0xFF)\ncmd(0x10)\nfor i in range(40000):\n    data(0xFF)\n\ncmd(0x13)\nfor i in range(40000):\n    data(0x00)\n\n# Refresh\ncmd(0x04)\ntime.sleep_ms(300)\ncmd(0x12)\nwait_busy()\n\nprint("Done")', name='Run', argv=[], id='cmd_70', local_cwd='/home/ironick')
