14:29:46.109 [MainThread] INFO    thonny.running: Prepared clean state for executing ToplevelCommand(args=['-c'], args_str='-c $EDITOR_CONTENT', cmd_line='%Run -c $EDITOR_CONTENT', tty_mode=True, source='import time\nfrom machine import Pin, SPI\n\nspi = SPI(0, baudrate=2000000, polarity=0, phase=0, sck=Pin(2), mosi=Pin(3))\n\n# All CS pins\nm1_cs = Pin(1, Pin.OUT, value=1)\ns1_cs = Pin(5, Pin.OUT, value=1)\nm2_cs = Pin(9, Pin.OUT, value=1)\ns2_cs = Pin(13, Pin.OUT, value=1)\n\n# DC pins\ndc1 = Pin(26, Pin.OUT)\ndc2 = Pin(27, Pin.OUT)\n\n# Reset pins\nrst1 = Pin(21, Pin.OUT)\nrst2 = Pin(22, Pin.OUT)\n\n# Reset all\nfor r in [rst1, rst2]:\n    r.value(1)\n    time.sleep_ms(200)\n    r.value(0)\n    time.sleep_ms(10)\n    r.value(1)\n    time.sleep_ms(200)\n\ndef cmd_all(c):\n    dc1.value(0)\n    dc2.value(0)\n    for cs in [m1_cs, s1_cs, m2_cs, s2_cs]:\n        cs.value(0)\n    spi.write(bytearray([c]))\n    for cs in [m1_cs, s1_cs, m2_cs, s2_cs]:\n        cs.value(1)\n\ndef data_all(d):\n    dc1.value(1)\n    dc2.value(1)\n    for cs in [m1_cs, s1_cs, m2_cs, s2_cs]:\n        cs.value(0)\n    spi.write(bytearray([d]))\n    for cs in [m1_cs, s1_cs, m2_cs, s2_cs]:\n        cs.value(1)\n\n# Init all panels\ncmd_all(0x00)\ndata_all(0x0f)\n\ncmd_all(0x04)  # Power on\ntime.sleep_ms(300)\ncmd_all(0x12)  # Refresh\n\nprint("Sent refresh to all panels")', name='Run', argv=[], id='cmd_86', local_cwd='/home/ironick')
