15:00:18.030 [MainThread] INFO    thonny.running: Prepared clean state for executing ToplevelCommand(args=['-c'], args_str='-c $EDITOR_CONTENT', cmd_line='%Run -c $EDITOR_CONTENT', tty_mode=True, source='#!/usr/bin/python\n# -*- coding:utf-8 -*-\n\nimport sys\nimport framebuf\nfrom lib import epd12in48b_V2\nimport time\n\nprint("12.48inch e-paper B Demo...")\nepd = epd12in48b_V2.EPD()\n# Initialize library.\nepd.Init()\n\n# Clear epdlay.\nprint("clearing...")\nepd.clear()\n\nprint("drawing...")\n\ntime.sleep(2)\n\nprint("open pic...")\n# Create framebuffers (1-bit, white = 1, black = 0)\nwidth = epd12in48b_V2.EPD_WIDTH\nheight = epd12in48b_V2.EPD_HEIGHT\n\nblack_buf = bytearray(width * height // 8)\nred_buf = bytearray(width * height // 8)\n\nblack_fb = framebuf.FrameBuffer(black_buf, width, height, framebuf.MONO_HMSB)\nred_fb = framebuf.FrameBuffer(red_buf, width, height, framebuf.MONO_HMSB)\n\n# Fill white (1)\nblack_fb.fill(1)\nred_fb.fill(1)\n\n# Draw on black layer\nblack_fb.rect(40, 40, 400, 400, 0)  # x, y, w, h, color\nblack_fb.fill_rect(43, 43, 394, 394, 1)  # fill white\nblack_fb.line(40, 40, 440, 440, 0)\nblack_fb.line(440, 40, 40, 440, 0)\n\n# Draw on red layer\nred_fb.ellipse(240, 240, 190, 190, 0)  # cx, cy, rx, ry, color (approx arc)\nred_fb.text(\'Nick has done it team\', 600, 90, 0)\nred_fb.text(\'Test\', 600, 170, 0)\nred_fb.text(\'\', 600, 250, 0)\n\nepd.display(black_buf, red_buf)\ntime.sleep(2)\n\n# Do not use for a long time, please save the white screen to save\nprint("clearing and go to sleep...")\nepd.clear()\nepd.EPD_Sleep()\n\n\n', name='Run', argv=[], id='cmd_207', local_cwd='/home/ironick')
