15:44:35.951 [MainThread] INFO    thonny.running: Prepared clean state for executing ToplevelCommand(args=['-c'], args_str='-c $EDITOR_CONTENT', cmd_line='%Run -c $EDITOR_CONTENT', tty_mode=True, source='from lib import epd12in48b_V2\nimport time\nimport framebuf\n\nepd = epd12in48b_V2.EPD()\nepd.Init()\n\nwidth = epd12in48b_V2.EPD_WIDTH\nheight = epd12in48b_V2.EPD_HEIGHT\n\n# Create buffers\nblack_buf = bytearray(width * height // 8)\nred_buf = bytearray(width * height // 8)\n\nblack_fb = framebuf.FrameBuffer(black_buf, width, height, framebuf.MONO_HLSB)\nred_fb = framebuf.FrameBuffer(red_buf, width, height, framebuf.MONO_HLSB)\n\n# Fill white background\nblack_fb.fill(1)\nred_fb.fill(1)\n\n# Draw black rectangle on M1 section (rows 492-983, cols 0-647)\nblack_fb.fill_rect(0, 492, 648, 492, 0)\n\nepd.display(black_buf, red_buf)\ntime.sleep(2)\nepd.EPD_Sleep()\nprint("Done")', name='Run', argv=[], id='cmd_451', local_cwd='/home/ironick')
